WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.597
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.597 --> 00:00:04.393
Welcome to Unit 4, The Big Sky.

3
00:00:04.393 --> 00:00:08.386
This unit has 31 vocabulary cards in 5 learning groups.

4
00:00:08.386 --> 00:00:10.782
Group 1 is Shadows and Light.

5
00:00:10.782 --> 00:00:14.775
Listen for words such as shadow, light, sun, source, block.

6
00:00:14.775 --> 00:00:17.969
Group 2 is Sky and Time of Day.

7
00:00:17.969 --> 00:00:22.362
Listen for words such as sky, morning, midday, evening, sunrise, sunset.

8
00:00:22.362 --> 00:00:25.157
Group 3 is In the Big Sky.

9
00:00:25.157 --> 00:00:29.550
Listen for words such as moon, star, cloud, day, night, Earth.

10
00:00:29.550 --> 00:00:31.946
Group 4 is Describing Words (Adjectives).

11
00:00:31.946 --> 00:00:36.338
Listen for words such as long, short, high, low, bright, dark.

12
00:00:36.338 --> 00:00:38.335
Group 5 is Weather Words.

13
00:00:38.335 --> 00:00:42.328
Listen for words such as sunny, cloudy, windy, rainy, dry.

14
00:00:42.328 --> 00:00:52.311
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

15
00:00:52.311 --> 00:00:55.106
You are ready to begin Unit 4.
